Retrieves all `Answers` for the given `Question` on an `Event`.

`<%= "GET #{config[:api_endpoint]}/:account_slug/:event_slug/questions/:question_slug/answers" %>`

* `account_slug` - The `slug` attribute of an `Account`.
* `event_slug` - The `slug` attribute of an `Event`.
* `question_slug` - The `slug` attribute of a `Question`.
